title: Jamie Chung
summary: Jamie Jilynn Chung (born April 10, 1983) is an American actress and former reality television personality. She began her career in 2004 as a cast member on the MTV reality series The Real World: San Diego and subsequently through her appearances on its spin-off show, Real World/Road Rules Challenge: The InfernoÂ II. She is regarded by many as the Real World alumna with the most successful media career.[3][4]
